cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

The paper deals with facial pose and shape estimation from annotated images using convolutional neural networks and recurrent layers. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of reprojection errors and merging annotations from different sources also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) subfields.
